# Wedding FAQ
The venue is yours for 12 hours between 9 AM and 11 PM. Music needs to be turned off at 10 PM with one hour to clean up by 11 PM. If you want more than 12 hours of time on the property for the day of the event, then the fee is $750 per hour. #### How long do I get the venue for? We will evaluate each ceremony and event to do our best and arrange a time frame that works for you. #### What if my wedding start time is earlier in the day?
